.SH NAME
SDL_HINT_VITA_PVR_OPENGL \- A variable controlling whether OpenGL should be used instead of OpenGL ES on the PlayStation Vita\[char46]
.SH HEADER FILE
Defined in SDL3/SDL_hints\[char46]h

